These are Puzzles for 4x2 Level 8

.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-8-1::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: coffee, tea
The people use 2 different means of transport: bus, tram
City: colone, london
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: action, sports
1. the person watching action movies is not to the right of the person driving the tram##8
2. the person driving the tram is somewhere to the left of the person traveling to colone##5
3. the person drinking coffee is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |      2      |
| Beverage      | tea     | coffee      |
| Transport          | tram | bus    |
| City         | london   | colone |
| Movie-Genre   | action  | sports      |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-8-2::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, iced-tea
2 different pets are kept: turtle, guinea-pig
The people have 2 different jobs:  librarian, software-developer
House: futuristic, victorian
1. the person drinking iced-tea is on the far right##1
2. the owner of the turtle is somewhere to the left of the librarian##5
3. the software-developer is not to the right of the librarian##8
4. the futuristic house is not the owner of the guinea-pig##6

.:: Answer ::.
|             |         1          |      2      |
| Beverage    | almond-milk        | iced-tea    |
| Pet       | turtle         | guinea-pig |
| Job         | software-developer | librarian   |
| House   | futuristic               | victorian  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-8-3::.
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: epic, thriller
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: folk, metal
2 different games are played: scrabble, backgammon
The people grow 2 different varities of flowers: poppy, daisy
1. the person playing scrabble is in an odd position##4
2. the person playing backgammon is not to the right of the person who growsdaisy##8
3. the fan of folk is somewhere to the left of the person watching thriller movies##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2     |
| Movie-Genre   | epic       | thriller |
| Music-Genre   | folk       | metal    |
| Game   | scrabble | backgammon |
| Flower           | poppy        | daisy   |

