2. the person who's sport is basketball is not to the right of the person who's hobby is photography##8
3. the person who's hobby is photography is on the right of the person who's hobby is traveling##1
4. the person who's sport is basketball is on the left of the person eating papaya##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2      |
